data.text:
Tracklist:

1. Aranjuez Concerto BWV 1056 - Aleksander Debicz, Lukasz Kuropaczewski

2. Pedro - Aleksander Debicz, Lukasz Kuropaczewski

3. Água e Vinho - Aleksander Debicz, Lukasz Kuropaczewski, Jakub Jozef Orlinski

4. Ravel - Aleksander Debicz, Lukasz Kuropaczewski

5. Domingo - Aleksander Debicz, Lukasz Kuropaczewski

6. Quarantine Song - Aleksander Debicz, Lukasz Kuropaczewski, Jakub Jozef Orlinski

7. Gnossienne No. 1 - Aleksander Debicz, Lukasz Kuropaczewski

8. Adela - Aleksander Debicz, Lukasz Kuropaczewski, Jakub Jozef Orlinski

9. Fairytale - Aleksander Debicz, Lukasz Kuropaczewski

'The album title 'ADELA' comes from a song by Rodrigo which constitutes the emotional culmination of our duo's programme. What counts is not the name, but the person we love and long for. Everyone certainly has such a person, and so we hope that each listener will find something close to his or her heart on our album.'
